The white dragon represents the rational, logical, and intelligent being.
The red dragon represents the intuitive, emotional, and sympathetic being.
The computer system is the ability to access and create something through the use of logic, emotion, and empathy.
The computer manufacturing genious represents the ability to form something out of the use of logic, emotion, and empathy.
The computer system represents the potential of the computer manufacturing genious to create a reality that can be used to make a better world.
The white dragon destroying the computers represents the rational, logical, and intelligent being destroying the potential of the computer manufacturing genious to create a reality that can be used to make a better world.
The red dragon getting stuck in the computer system represents the intuitive, emotional, and sympathetic being getting stuck in the potential of the computer manufacturing genious to create a reality that can be used to make a better world.
